name: Sabrina Trinidad Panlilio
text: I still say it counts as a dishonorable discharge! Nakalagay "dishonorable discharge from service" NOT "dishonorable discharge from MILITARY service". As president, it would count as "dishonorable discharge from PUBLIC service"
